{"tid":2297633,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有人同我一樣對生活好麻木","createTime":"2020-11-23T11:54:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T12:11:14.000Z","uid":142716,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"36d735627e9c26da7224182d14945f32363a331e","tid":2297633,"uid":142716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T11:54:57.000Z","msg":"純粹係對自己人生無期望<br />\n<br />\n由細到大都特別想理想同目標<br />\n人越大就越覺得唔知生活為左咩<br />\n連少少期望都無埋<br />\n對好多事都無感覺<br />\n好耐無真心咁好開心笑過<br />\n同時都無因為啲咩事唔開心<br />\n連驚 緊張 嬲 都好似好耐無試過<br />\n好耐無試過對人有心動既感覺 即使有人追<br />\n完全唔會憧憬將來 結婚生仔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n9up完<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df7517a6624f32b05d020ffc59192a73ce1915f","tid":2297633,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T11:55:24.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"61f7e8e65d4ae2d7f3af6a96f041dff27331b954","tid":2297633,"uid":23715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T11:56:27.000Z","msg":"我諗有另一半同共同目標，會更好"},{"pid":"a63b2a03fe129ae81d75ecf0b5391b6186f735b2","tid":2297633,"uid":269372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T11:56:59.000Z","msg":"加油 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe094a41abe81aa16473c9455dad32cf6af84e39","tid":2297633,"uid":358571,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T11:57:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e339c2ce2234cd01af92eba01b349142b69a1d56","tid":2297633,"uid":142716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8df7517a6624f32b05d020ffc59192a73ce1915f","tid":2297633,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T11:55:24.000Z","msg":"加油"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T11:58:03.000Z","msg":"多謝你先<br />\n<br />\n不過其實都無乜需要加油既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"